
"smart_sources:_000.General/Discipline Eats Motivation For Breakfast..md": {"path":"_000.General/Discipline Eats Motivation For Breakfast..md","last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"last_read":{"hash":"1qequiy","at":1772113914228},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1772025361643,"size":1957,"at":1772113914229,"hash":"1qequiy"},"blocks":{"#":[1,6],"##{1}":[1,1],"##{2}":[2,2],"##{3}":[3,3],"##{4}":[4,4],"##{5}":[5,5],"##":[7,24],"###{1}":[8,9],"###{2}":[10,11],"###{3}":[12,13],"###{4}":[14,15],"###{5}":[16,17],"###{6}":[18,19],"###{7}":[20,21],"###{8}":[22,23],"###{9}":[24,24]},"outlinks":[{"title":"Jocko Willink","target":"Jocko Willink","line":2},{"title":"Comfort Zone","target":"Comfort Zone","line":4},{"title":"Compound Interest","target":"Compound Interest","line":4},{"title":"Discipline","target":"Discipline","line":4},{"title":"Purpose; Mindset; Motivation; Willpower","target":"Purpose; Mindset; Motivation; Willpower","line":4},{"title":"Taking Action","target":"Taking Action","line":4},{"title":"The moment the alarm goes off is the first test; it sets the tone for the rest of the day. The test is not a complex one when the alarm goes off, do you get up out of bed, or do you lie there in comfort and fall back to sleep","target":"The moment the alarm goes off is the first test; it sets the tone for the rest of the day. The test is not a complex one when the alarm goes off, do you get up out of bed, or do you lie there in comfort and fall back to sleep","line":8},{"title":"The difference between good and great results is often found in consistently doing the boring things you know you should do exactly when you feel like doing them the least.","target":"The difference between good and great results is often found in consistently doing the boring things you know you should do exactly when you feel like doing them the least.","line":10},{"title":"“Everything can be taken from a man but one thing - the last of the human freedoms  to choose one’s attitude in any given set of circumstances, to choose one’s own way.” -Viktor Frankl","target":"“Everything can be taken from a man but one thing - the last of the human freedoms  to choose one’s attitude in any given set of circumstances, to choose one’s own way.” -Viktor Frankl","line":12},{"title":"if you want to reach a goal, you need to do two things- make the things that will help you reach the goal stronger, and reduce the things that will stop you from reaching the goal.","target":"if you want to reach a goal, you need to do two things- make the things that will help you reach the goal stronger, and reduce the things that will stop you from reaching the goal.","line":14},{"title":"“Just start working. If you feel that you just can’t write or you’re too tired or this, that, and the other, just stop thinking about it, and go and work. Life doesn’t have to be so overthought. You don’t have to wait to be inspired. ”","target":"“Just start working. If you feel that you just can’t write or you’re too tired or this, that, and the other, just stop thinking about it, and go and work. Life doesn’t have to be so overthought. You don’t have to wait to be inspired. ”","line":16},{"title":" \"I never doubted not only that I would get out, but also that I would prevail in the end and turn the experience into the defining event of my life, which, in retrospect, I would not trade.” -Jim Stockdale","target":"I never doubted not only that I would get out, but also that I would prevail in the end and turn the experience into the defining event of my life, which, in retrospect, I would not trade.”","line":18},{"title":"Line up at least one task today with your mission, and things will happen.","target":"Line up at least one task today with your mission, and things will happen.","line":20},{"title":"Prepared person is positioned to benefit from unexpected opportunities","target":"Prepared person is positioned to benefit from unexpected opportunities","line":22},{"title":"Is easier to do something every day than a few times a week. Every day - default behavior","target":"Is easier to do something every day than a few times a week. Every day - default behavior","line":24}],"metadata":{"tags":["#quote","#🌿"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
